dk is a 2015 indian kannada satirical film directed by vijay kampali , formerly known as udaya prakash , who also directed kalla malla sulla and auto raja .   produced by actress rakshita , the film stars prem and chaitra chandranath in the lead roles .   actress sunny leone features in a special item song sesamma , which marks her kannada film debut .   the film 's score and soundtrack was composed by arjun janya , and the first kannada film to feature 7.1 surround sound .   the film opened across karnataka on 13 february 2015 .